(3, '2014-07-28 22:32:49', 'Jacqui', 'Long', 'jacqui@thestartupshirt.com', 'They''re Like A Permanent Advertising Campaign\r\n\r\nHello, \r\n\r\nT-shirts are like walking billboards. They''re worn and seen by everyone, everywhere, all the time. Frequency is one of the hallmarks of advertising success. \r\n\r\nGive them to your clients, employees, service providers, fans, and anyone else who deserves your attitude of gratitude. They''ll wear them like a badge of honor while consistently promoting you to new prospects. \r\n\r\nWe''ll provide you with custom, high quality T-shirts and other promotional products with a quick turnaround and solid customer service. We''re also in your backyard. \r\n\r\nI''d love to chat about your promotional needs, so give me a call or hop on the site for a free quote. www.thestartupshirt.com \r\n\r\nThanks for your time,\r\n\r\nJacqui Long : Account Manager\r\n720.931.6878\r\njacqui@thestartupshirt.com\r\nwww.thestartupshirt.com \r\n\r\nIf you''d like to opt out of these emails, hit reply and type unsubscribe.', 0),
(4, '2014-12-18 22:18:40', 'David', 'Thomas', 'david.seoweb@gmail.com', 'Cirrusidea.com Team,\r\n\r\nI thought you might like to know some of the reasons why you are not getting enough Social Media and Organic search engine traffic for Cirrusidea.com\r\n\r\n1. Your website Cirrusidea.com is not ranking top in Google organic search for many competitive keyword phrases.\r\n\r\n2. Your website profile is not available in most of the Social Media Websites.\r\n\r\n3. Your site has low Google back links, this can be improved further.\r\n\r\nThere might be a couple of reasons behind it. For that only you are not getting enough Organic search engine and Social Media traffic for your site. There are many additional improvements that could be made to your website to drive more traffic and getting it more visible in search engine through organic way.\r\n\r\nWe are giving World class service with guaranteed results within given time to our client''s cause we have an effective team with the best experts in the SEO market. Being in the Google Organic position it is the best thing you can do for your companys website traffic and online reputation.\r\n\r\nI found your site in the Google search and after having a look over your website, I think you should go for an SEO campaign to boost your marketing strategy.\r\n\r\nSounds interesting? Feel free to email us or alternatively you can provide me with your phone number and the best time to call you.\r\n\r\n-------------------------------------\r\n\r\nBest Regards,\r\n\r\nDavid Thomas\r\nSEO Consultant\r\n\r\nSkype ID\r\nsmwebguru\r\n-------------------------------------\r\n\r\nPS1: This is a one time email and you may ask us to REMOVE you from our mailing list.\r\n\r\nPS2: I found your site from online advertising, but did not click.\r\n\r\nPS3: We operate 24 x7. I will be happy to send you links to price list.\r\n\r\nHow we are different from others and Why should you choose us ?\r\n\r\non receiving a response from you we will clarify you.', 0),
(5, '2015-04-16 16:59:44', 'Hayley', 'Samela', 'hayley_samela@condenast.com', 'Hi, \r\n\r\nHappy Thursday! In coming across Cirrus Idea, I wanted to introduce myself and reach out to learn more about your digital marketing initiatives as your company is a prime example of a web service Ars Technica readers would be interested in. Ars readers are new technology influentials and business decision makers who look for new applications and platforms to enhance their business. \r\n\r\nTo give you some more background, Arstechnica.com is part of the WIRED Media Division here at Conde Nast and is the most trusted source for new developments in the world of technology:\r\n\r\nArs has an audience of 13.0 million unique monthly visitors\r\n\r\nReaders of Ars are 2X more likely to be Business Decision Makers, IT professionals and work in Top Management\r\n\r\nRealizing your time is valuable, would you be available this Monday at 2 pm EST  to discuss more about  Cirrus Idea?\r\n\r\nBest,\r\n\r\nHayley Samela', 0);
