(449, '2013-01-09 19:46:21', 'Okay Ethan! I created this private folder for us to work on our CVT.  I have a relatively good model built showing some function and build viablility.  Lets work on this, maybe its our real value adding money maker.  I like the idea that you could install this thing on any normal bike. Unlike the NuVinci thing, you have to buy a new expensive ass bike to use...  I am sure there would be a ton of challenges to make this thing really work, but I think it is close to the point where we could MFG.com it to make a prototype.  Oh man also I have a sweet vendor I have to tell you about.  Oh, I get a new phone today, so I\\''ll call you when I get it, and we need to meet up. In the meantime, open up variabletrans.asm.', 'variabletrans.zip', 1, '/files/Engineering/Mechanical Engineering/CVT EWTG', 6877189, 0),
