(499, '2013-02-06 21:45:31', 'At Paradigm Motion we strive for excellence in customer service and being the hardest working contract Business/Engineering service your money can buy.\n\nIf you or your company needs a part manufactured at the best price or you need 3D modeling, drafting or analysis for your part; we specialize in getting you your parts with the most cost effective and efficient design for the job.\n\nIf your company needs Engineering analysis for your design, we provide solutions to analyze your static, dynamic and thermal systems.\n\nIf your product needs are in computer software development, we can also produce customized packages.\n\nIf you or your company need anything in the product development cycle from concept to market release we can help you with the entire product development cycle.\nConcept art\nEngineering Design and Drafting\nWebsite design\nPackaging\nDistribution\n\nWe are here to help develop out of the box ideas.  ', '', 1, '/files/Business/Paradigm Motion', 0, 5),
