(500, '2013-02-06 21:46:01', 'Services:\nProject Management\nWorking on a new product that needs to get through the pipeline? We can help push it through and make your project a success.\n\n3D Design\nWe can help you bring your ideas to life and design the widget in CAD space where it can be turned into a reality.\n(SolidWorks 2012) \n\nFEA Analysis\nNot sure if your part is up for its job? Let our Finite Element and Engineering analysis mitigate any doubts in your part before it is put into production.\n(LISA FEA 6.0) \n\nDrafting\nDo you have the model but not a print, let us do your draft to help get your part into production. We will provide a print with necessary GD&T.\n(SolidWorks 2012) \n\nPart and assembly acquisition\nSubmit your parts and assemblies for quotation, and we can work to get you the best price and lead time.\n\nPart Machining and Prototyping\nWant to bring your 3D or 2D design to reality, We can do it for you.\n(BOB-CAD/CAM v23) \n\nSoftware Development\nIf it is data crunching or even a routine task that needs automation; we can help you with a custom software to make your life easier.\n(C++ and VB Applications) \n\nConcept Art and Rendering\nIf you want to see a rendering of your idea, we want to bring your invention or concept to life on paper.\n(GIMP) \n\nWebsite Design and Management\nLet us build and maintain your professional looking static and dynimic websites.\n(PHP, MySQL, HTML, JavScrip) ', '', 1, '/files/Business/Paradigm Motion', 0, 5),
